<span id="freeTextContainer2482158926829031413"><strong>Lovely and different </strong><br/><br/>Although I hated Daisy for a big chunk of this book but I really wanted to visit her bistro someday.<br/>It&apos;s a very charming story set in Paris with witty characters. The turn of the events were unpredictable and some were serious. <br/>I loved it</span>
  <span id="freeText2482158926829031413" style="display:none"><strong>Lovely and different </strong><br /><br />Although I hated Daisy for a big chunk of this book but I really wanted to visit her bistro someday.<br />It's a very charming story set in Paris with witty characters. The turn of the events were unpredictable and some were serious. <br />I loved it</span>
