  <span id="freeText5175914537452755923" style="display:none">Just another poor selection on my part when Amazon grants the prime members a free monthly book. I do not believe I have ever managed to select one I could bear reading. Back to the library for me.<br />Dec 19, 2017 edit:<br />I felt like giving this book another try since I had owned it since Aug 2017 and the year is coming to a close.<br />Yes, it is a romance and somewhat comic and had more merit than I originally gave it credit for. I am glad I went back to read again as it did amuse me. There were some realistic struggles for the American fiction writer living in Paris and some interesting life decision struggles for the English movie star hiding out from a painful marriage with her friend in Paris. Yes, they meet.<br />Nothing wrong with a happy ending now and again.</span>
